high_descs: walk to face the kitchen sinks
pick up the butter knife from the counter left of the sinks
walk slightly to the right to face counter to the right of the sinks
put the butter knife in the pan to the very right of the counter
pick up the pan and the ladle with the aqua handle
walk slightly left to face the sinks and counter left of the sinks
place the ladle and pan into the right most sink basin
anns.task_desc: put a ladle, pan, and knife into a kitchen sink basin

high_descs: Turn to your left and walk to the sink.
Pick up the butter knife to the front, left of the sink, on the counter.
Move over to your right so that you are in front of the counter to the right of the sink.
Place the knife on the pan that is on the counter, with the ladle.
Pick up the pan with the knife and ladle.
Move over to your left so that you are in front of the large sink, on the right.
Place the pan with the knife and ladle, in the large sink on the right.
anns.task_desc: Put a pan containing a knife and ladle in the sink.

high_descs: Turn left and head towards the sink.
Pick up the knife to the left of the sink.
Take a step to the right from where you are at.
Place the knife on the gold plate with the gold scoop.
Pick up the plate along with the knife and scoop.
Take a step to the left from where you are at.
Place the plate along with the knife and scoop in the right sink.
anns.task_desc: Place the plate along with the knife and scoop in the right sink.
